{
  "$comment": [
    "Davidup v0.4 — 60-second clip built from 4 scenes (intro / two sections / outro).",
    "The root file is the whole video at a glance: pure sequencing + crossfades.",
    "Each scene file lives next door and owns its own ~50-line motion script.",
    "",
    "How it stitches together:",
    "  imports[]  — pulls each scene definition file in via $ref (§5)",
    "  scenes     — receives those definitions keyed by their `id`",
    "  items[*].type='scene' — places each scene as an instance with params + transform",
    "  tweens[]   — only crossfades on the wrapper-group's transform.opacity",
    "",
    "Tween count for sequencing: 7. Total motion shipped on screen: ~30 (the rest",
    "live inside scene files). Compare to the v0.1 one-file approach which would",
    "need every motion authored at the root."
  ],

  "version": "0.2",

  "composition": {
    "width": 1280,
    "height": 720,
    "fps": 30,
    "duration": 60,
    "background": "#000000"
  },

  "assets": [
    { "id": "font-display", "type": "font", "src": "./fonts/BebasNeue-Regular.ttf", "family": "DavidupDisplay" }
  ],

  "scenes": {
    "introCard": { "$ref": "./scenes/intro.json" },
    "sectionOne": { "$ref": "./scenes/section-one.json" },
    "sectionTwo": { "$ref": "./scenes/section-two.json" },
    "outroCard": { "$ref": "./scenes/outro.json" }
  },

  "layers": [
    { "id": "stage", "z": 0, "opacity": 1, "blendMode": "normal", "items": ["intro", "act1", "act2", "outro"] }
  ],

  "items": {
    "intro": {
      "type": "scene",
      "scene": "introCard",
      "params": { "title": "DAVIDUP", "subtitle": "v0.4 · scenes", "fontDisplay": "font-display" },
      "transform": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "scaleX": 1, "scaleY": 1, "rotation": 0, "anchorX": 0, "anchorY": 0, "opacity": 0 }
    },
    "act1": {
      "type": "scene",
      "scene": "sectionOne",
      "start": 12,
      "params": { "header": "I. Bouncing rail", "fontDisplay": "font-display" },
      "transform": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "scaleX": 1, "scaleY": 1, "rotation": 0, "anchorX": 0, "anchorY": 0, "opacity": 0 }
    },
    "act2": {
      "type": "scene",
      "scene": "sectionTwo",
      "start": 30,
      "params": { "header": "II. Spinning satellite", "fontDisplay": "font-display" },
      "transform": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "scaleX": 1, "scaleY": 1, "rotation": 0, "anchorX": 0, "anchorY": 0, "opacity": 0 }
    },
    "outro": {
      "type": "scene",
      "scene": "outroCard",
      "start": 48,
      "params": { "footer": "60s · 4 scenes · 1280x720 · 30fps", "fontDisplay": "font-display" },
      "transform": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "scaleX": 1, "scaleY": 1, "rotation": 0, "anchorX": 0, "anchorY": 0, "opacity": 0 }
    }
  },

  "tweens": [
    { "id": "intro_in", "target": "intro", "property": "transform.opacity", "from": 0, "to": 1, "start": 0, "duration": 0.5 },
    { "id": "intro_out", "target": "intro", "property": "transform.opacity", "from": 1, "to": 0, "start": 11.5, "duration": 0.5 },
    { "id": "act1_in", "target": "act1", "property": "transform.opacity", "from": 0, "to": 1, "start": 12, "duration": 0.5 },
    { "id": "act1_out", "target": "act1", "property": "transform.opacity", "from": 1, "to": 0, "start": 29.5, "duration": 0.5 },
    { "id": "act2_in", "target": "act2", "property": "transform.opacity", "from": 0, "to": 1, "start": 30, "duration": 0.5 },
    { "id": "act2_out", "target": "act2", "property": "transform.opacity", "from": 1, "to": 0, "start": 47.5, "duration": 0.5 },
    { "id": "outro_in", "target": "outro", "property": "transform.opacity", "from": 0, "to": 1, "start": 48, "duration": 0.5 }
  ]
}
